Exercise1
Set an attribute for a symbol f so that f[{1,2},{3,4}] evaluates to \
{f[1,3],f[2,4]}
.\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9856523125196857`*^9, 
  3.9856523221785736`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"927919bc-5d17-6342-a678-\
4eda08256386"],

